                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "title": "The Paris Agreement",
                  "body": "Adopted in 2015 at COP 21, the Paris Agreement aims to limit global warming to well below 2 degrees Celsius above pre-industrial levels, aiming for 1.5 degrees."
