                      "date": "2009",
                      "title": "Copenhagen Accord",
                      "description": "Recognized the scientific view that the increase in global temperature should be below 2°C."
                    },
                    {
                      "date": "2015",
                      "title": "Paris Agreement",
                      "description": "Legally binding international treaty adopted by 196 Parties."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "warning",
                  "body": "The Montreal Protocol (1987) is often confused with climate change treaties, but it was specifically designed to protect the ozone layer, not directly limit warming."
